c:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131968705,imgsize-1113380.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lavrov says Russia won't bend again on Ukraine, cites talks with Trump in Alaska]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131965981.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[According to Lavrov, Putin agreed to proposals put forward by the United States during the Alaska meeting and reached an understanding with Trump on how the fighting in Ukraine could be brought to an end and how broader discussions could proceed afterwards. Lavrov said Russia remained committed to those agreements and would not support alternative interim arrangements or bend to ultimatums.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-already-compromised-lavrov-says-russia-wont-bend-again-on-ukraine-cites-talks-with-trump-in-alaska/articleshow/131965981.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-already-compromised-lavrov-says-russia-wont-bend-again-on-ukraine-cites-talks-with-trump-in-alaska/articleshow/131965981.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T16:36:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131966039,imgsize-66021.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UN watchdog chief says Iran's nuclear inspections 'going to happen'; Tehran rebuts]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131967291.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iranian officials were quick to rebut Rafael Grossi's, the chief of the UN nuclear watchdog, remark as deputy foreign minister Kazem Gharibabadi said no agreement had been reached on inspections of the facilities attacked during the conflict and stressed that any future access would depend on a comprehensive settlement between Tehran and Washington. "Obviously, to do that, we will have to inspect," Grossi said.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-watchdog-chief-says-irans-nuclear-inspections-going-to-happen-tehran-rebuts/articleshow/131967291.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-watchdog-chief-says-irans-nuclear-inspections-going-to-happen-tehran-rebuts/articleshow/131967291.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T17:23:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131967338,imgsize-84446.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Melinda Gates: "A woman with a voice is by definition a strong woman. But the search to find…”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131965944.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-melinda-gates-a-woman-with-a-voice-is-by-definition-a-strong-woman-but-the-search-to-find/articleshow/131965944.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-melinda-gates-a-woman-with-a-voice-is-by-definition-a-strong-woman-but-the-search-to-find/articleshow/131965944.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T16:36:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131966044,imgsize-70710.cms"/></item></channel></rss>